  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"entry entryPage\">\n   <p class=\"mobile-date-eyebrow\">18th May 2026</p>\n   <div class=\"beat beat-sighting\">\n    <div class=\"beat-content\">\n     <div class=\"beat-row1\">\n      <span class=\"beat-label sighting\">Sighting</span> <span class=\"beat-title\"><a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/362782049\">7:51 AM – 8:13 AM</a></span> <span class=\"beat-commit\">— Glaucous-winged Gull, Brown Pelican, Snowy Egret, Canada Goose, in Los Angeles River, CA, US</span>\n     </div>\n     <figure>\n      <a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161673/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161673/small.jpg\" alt=\"Glaucous-winged Gull\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n      <figcaption>\n       <a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/362782049\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">Glaucous-winged Gull</a>\n      </figcaption>\n     </figure>\n     <figure>\n      <a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161721/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161721/small.jpg\" alt=\"Glaucous-winged Gull\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n      <figcaption>\n       <a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/362782049\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">Glaucous-winged Gull</a>\n      </figcaption>\n     </figure>\n     <figure>\n      <a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161937/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161937/small.jpg\" alt=\"Brown Pelican\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n      <figcaption>\n       <a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/362782164\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">Brown Pelican</a>\n      </figcaption>\n     </figure>\n     <figure>\n      <a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161148/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161148/small.jpg\" alt=\"Snowy Egret\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n      <figcaption>\n       <a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/362781792\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">Snowy Egret</a>\n      </figcaption>\n     </figure>\n     <figure>\n      <a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161189/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662161189/small.jpg\" alt=\"Snowy Egret\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n      <figcaption>\n       <a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/362781792\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">Snowy Egret</a>\n      </figcaption>\n     </figure>\n     <figure>\n      <a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662160828/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662160828/small.jpg\" alt=\"Canada Goose\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n      <figcaption>\n       <a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/362781627\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">Canada Goose</a>\n      </figcaption>\n     </figure>\n     <figure>\n      <a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662160866/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/662160866/small.jpg\" alt=\"Canada Goose\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n      <figcaption>\n       <a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/362781627\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">Canada Goose</a>\n      </figcaption>\n     </figure>\n     <div class=\"beat-note blogmark-body\">\n      <p>I'm heading home from PyCon US today so I went on a last morning walk to try and spot a pelican. I saw one! Didn't get a great photo but I did also see some goslings down by the swan boat lake.</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"edit-page-link\" style=\"display: none;\"></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
